title: Let’s take this campaign to the next level!
description: Hi all, I just wanted to reach out to let you know we’ve just passed 106 signatures on our petition! Thank you so much for your support! Will you help me to get more support by sharing this petition with ten other people? If enough of us sign we can’t be ignored! Here’s a link to share https://www.change.org/p/warner-brothers-domestic-abuse-affects-millions-of-men-double-standards-need-to-end-justiceforjohnnydepp

title: Still hoping to get the first 20!

description:
5 signatures within the first minutes was so great and in the first hour approaching 20!
